name: blue printed top from lefties, in Madrid
description:
I bought this shirt while I was in Spain earlier this summer before trying it on and it turns out it didn't cover my chest enough and my boobies spilled out! (I'm a 36D)

Size large, brand new with tags. The only time it was worn was when I tried it on.

100% polyester. Very soft and comfortable.

care instructions:
machine wash up to 30C/86F
do not bleach
tumble dry low
iron up to 110C/230F
iron inside out
dry clean perchloroethylene (whatever the f that means)
